26:32.966 --> 26:34.259
and they went and got ice cream,

26:34.342 --> 26:36.344
came back and continued beating me.

26:36.428 --> 26:38.763
And what happened to the boys
who beat you up?

26:38.847 --> 26:41.975
Well, they all became senators.
Every single one of them.

26:42.058 --> 26:42.809
Name one.

26:43.310 --> 26:44.728
Dianne Feinstein.

26:48.273 --> 26:49.607
Was the head bully.

26:50.483 --> 26:51.609
Beat me savagely.

26:51.693 --> 26:52.902
It doesn't make any sense.

26:52.986 --> 26:56.781
I'm starting to wonder if your name
is even Todd Caringtonbergenson.

26:56.865 --> 26:57.907
Oh, please.

26:57.991 --> 27:00.577
Todd, what is the state fish of Idaho?

27:00.660 --> 27:02.454
It is a…

27:03.038 --> 27:05.665
white-bellied cod.

27:05.749 --> 27:06.833
Wrong!

27:06.916 --> 27:08.335
It's the cutthroat trout.

27:08.418 --> 27:09.836
Well, who knows the state fish?

27:09.919 --> 27:12.172
This person is an imposter, ladies,

27:12.255 --> 27:15.091
and he's using the art of illusion

27:15.175 --> 27:17.302
to get us to have S-E-X.

27:17.385 --> 27:18.261
No!

27:18.345 --> 27:20.430
Get him! Mama! Mama!

27:20.513 --> 27:22.849
- Mama! Mama! Mama!
- Tittynope! Tittynope!

27:22.932 --> 27:24.267
<i>…just appeared then.</i>

27:24.351 --> 27:27.771
<i>Now, we have to do French drop</i>
<i>which is a ball transfer,</i>

27:27.854 --> 27:30.023
<i>reach forward again, and again you say,</i>

27:30.106 --> 27:32.984
<i>"Oh, is that another quarter in your ear?"</i>

27:33.068 --> 27:34.861
<i>Mama! Mama! Mama!</i>

27:35.445 --> 27:35.945
Conan.

27:36.446 --> 27:38.656
- <i>Tittynope. Tittynope.</i>
- Conan, what's going on? What's going on?

27:38.740 --> 27:40.909
- Tittynope! Tittynope!
- Mama! Mama!

27:40.992 --> 27:43.453
Alright, lock yourself
in a safe room, Conan.

27:43.536 --> 27:44.954
I'm coming to save you.

27:45.038 --> 27:47.415
- Tittynope!
- Mama! Mama! Mama!

27:52.545 --> 27:55.131
It's locked. We can wait him out, though.

27:55.840 --> 27:59.135
Ladies! There's a guy in the corner
asking kids to pick a card.

28:00.136 --> 28:01.304
Any card!

28:05.225 --> 28:09.104
Conan! It's senior detective,
Terry Seattle. You can come out now.

28:10.647 --> 28:11.481
You're safe.

28:12.565 --> 28:14.776
- You're safe. Are you okay?
- I'm okay. I'm okay. I'm good.

28:14.859 --> 28:16.152
All right, let's get the hell out of--

28:16.903 --> 28:18.279
Wow. Look at all these snacks.

28:18.363 --> 28:19.739
Let's grab some stuff, come on.

28:21.032 --> 28:23.743
They got plain tortillas.
I can never find plain tortillas.

28:23.827 --> 28:24.494
Well, they're pretty available.

28:24.577 --> 28:26.204
No, but every time
I go to the grocery store, I'm like,

28:26.287 --> 28:27.747
"Do you have any plain tortillas?"
they're like, "No, we're fresh out."

28:27.831 --> 28:29.290
They're very available.

28:29.374 --> 28:32.085
Everyone has plain tortillas.

28:32.168 --> 28:34.129
<i>It was time for Conan to decide</i>

28:34.212 --> 28:35.839
<i>who killed poor Sarah,</i>

28:35.922 --> 28:39.008
<i>so we lured the three suspects</i>
<i>back to the library</i>

28:39.092 --> 28:41.886
<i>under the guise of another magic show.</i>

28:43.471 --> 28:47.142
Ladies and gentlemen, we will not
be performing any illusions tonight.

28:47.642 --> 28:52.063
No, in fact, if anything,
we will be removing an illusion.

28:52.814 --> 28:53.732
The illusion

28:54.315 --> 28:55.859
of innocence.

28:56.359 --> 28:57.152
That's right.

28:57.652 --> 29:00.572
Before us here are these three top hats.

29:00.655 --> 29:02.657
In each one is the name of a suspect.

29:02.741 --> 29:03.950
My partner, Conan O'Brien,

29:04.033 --> 29:07.287
will now reveal who he believes
committed this murder.

29:07.370 --> 29:09.664
Conan, was it Deb,

29:10.165 --> 29:12.167
was it Magic Melvin,

29:12.667 --> 29:14.377
or was it Kathy?

29:14.878 --> 29:15.587
Conan,

29:16.463 --> 29:19.966
please choose who you think is the killer.

29:29.184 --> 29:30.518
The murderer…!

29:33.313 --> 29:35.315
Magic Melvin.

29:36.733 --> 29:37.317
No.

29:39.068 --> 29:40.612
What is going on here?

29:40.695 --> 29:43.072
Chief, we figured out who the killer is.

29:43.156 --> 29:44.491
Conan figured it out.

29:44.574 --> 29:48.077
I have all the logic
as to why it has to be Magic Melvin.

29:48.161 --> 29:51.247
I'm not sure exactly
why I dressed as a magician,

29:52.040 --> 29:54.292
but I am certain

29:55.251 --> 29:57.337
<i>he</i> is the murderer.

29:57.420 --> 29:59.088
And what is your evidence?

29:59.172 --> 30:00.256
Magic Melvin,

30:00.340 --> 30:03.593
you told us that you had
to go Scotchgard your rabbit.

30:04.302 --> 30:07.514
Maybe to keep hot sauce off the rabbit,

30:08.473 --> 30:11.392
because who leaves hot sauce
on a saw and no fingerprints?

30:12.435 --> 30:14.312
Why, sir, that is the act

30:15.980 --> 30:17.023
of a magician.

30:18.024 --> 30:19.317
I also think you had another motive.

30:19.400 --> 30:22.362
I think that Kathy is your mother.

30:22.987 --> 30:25.073
That you hate your mother

30:25.782 --> 30:27.909
and that because
she's turned her back on magic,

30:28.409 --> 30:29.661
you wanted to frame her.

30:30.370 --> 30:31.704
That part's pretty far-fetched.

30:31.788 --> 30:33.790
I'm the youngest person in this room.

30:34.415 --> 30:35.542
I understand.

30:35.625 --> 30:37.627
And I don't know
how the whole age thing works.

30:37.710 --> 30:39.003
I'm still working on that.

30:39.087 --> 30:41.130
It's very possible I could be your father.

30:41.631 --> 30:42.757
- Yeah.
- Age-wise.

30:43.258 --> 30:44.759
Conan O'Brien,

30:44.843 --> 30:48.304
it brings me no joy
to tell you that you are…

30:49.764 --> 30:51.140
100%…

30:55.812 --> 30:56.563
Correct.

30:56.646 --> 30:57.605
Yes!

30:58.231 --> 30:59.524
Yes!

30:59.607 --> 31:03.695
It was Magic Melvin
who killed the magician's assistant.

31:04.195 --> 31:08.408
You did notice that Melvin put hot sauce
on his breakfast burrito every morning.

31:08.491 --> 31:12.203
Three eggs soft scrambled,
onions, peppers, Tabasco--

31:12.287 --> 31:14.664
And owned a rabbit for his act.

31:14.747 --> 31:16.457
I have to Scotchgard my rabbit.

31:16.541 --> 31:19.878
We know it couldn't have been Deb.
She was allergic to pets.

31:19.961 --> 31:24.382
My boyfriend tried to cheer me up by
buying me a puppy, but I have allergies!

31:24.465 --> 31:27.051
Meanwhile Kathy
had more motive than anyone,

31:27.677 --> 31:29.762
but she didn't know
how to pick the lock on the door

31:29.846 --> 31:34.309
when you ran
like an overgrown gazelle for safety.

31:35.018 --> 31:36.019
It's locked.

31:36.102 --> 31:39.731
But you know who could pick a lock?
Magic Melvin.

31:39.814 --> 31:41.816
Especially on someone
who knows actual--

31:41.900 --> 31:44.777
- He did it!
- Thank you very much.

31:44.861 --> 31:48.072
Magic Melvin was the killer.

31:49.282 --> 31:50.491
Take him away.

31:51.910 --> 31:54.329
I only murdered her
'cause I wanted her dead!

31:54.913 --> 31:57.957
It's a very-- It's a good reason
to murder somebody.

31:58.917 --> 32:00.501
The handcuffs
are not going to work on him.

32:00.585 --> 32:02.253
Already, no handcuffs.

32:02.337 --> 32:05.173
Conan O'Brien, congratulations.

32:06.966 --> 32:08.760
Well, Conan, you did it.

32:10.094 --> 32:12.847
You solved the case,
even though your logic was…

32:13.556 --> 32:15.224
crazy nonsensical.

32:16.059 --> 32:18.061
But you make a fantastic cop.

32:20.021 --> 32:21.564
You know, I also learned something.

32:22.106 --> 32:23.942
I learned a little magic trick.

32:24.025 --> 32:24.901
You learned magic.

32:24.984 --> 32:27.737
That's right. Go ahead and sneeze.

32:29.238 --> 32:29.948
Here.

32:30.531 --> 32:32.617
Let me get you a handkerchief.

32:33.201 --> 32:33.826
Go ahead.

32:37.080 --> 32:38.831
I've got a handkerchief.

32:40.917 --> 32:43.628
It's not ending. It's not ending.

32:43.711 --> 32:45.254
This is legitimately not ending.

32:45.338 --> 32:47.131
- It's a lot of--
- I'm getting--

32:48.174 --> 32:50.635
Okay, you know what?
Now, I just hate magic. This is stupid.

32:51.219 --> 32:53.763
<i>On the next episode</i>
<i>of</i> Murderville…

32:53.846 --> 32:56.057
Terry say hi
to your new partner, Marshawn Lynch.

32:56.140 --> 32:58.184
- How much training have you had?
- I watched <i>Training Day</i>.

33:00.853 --> 33:02.981
This was the murder weapon.
